snippet.title: [Download] Star Revenge X - Discord Star Adventure - Release Video
snippet.description:
Long time no release... and then it's this too? Ever though that Weegee in SR1 wasn't enough? Yes? Then this hack is made for you. Enjoy 99 red coin stars on giant stars from my Discord server, with an additional star for getting all red coin stars.

DL: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jdZw3Su0sdJva2TCWHpHlrnUXAU1uIs6/view

You wouldn't know, how much pain it was to set up this hack in a ROM, this has a total of like 110 areas.
